_sText:
This is my first map released to public, i've made some aim maps for our clanserver, but they weren't worth releasing. I've played this map many many hours on Americas Army and i wanted to have it in Cs:s.
This is like the 7th version of my map but i recently managed to optimize it as much as possible. We've played the map enough on our server to test it for bugs and all bugs we found have been corrected. 
Please go easy on me! :P
Have fun with it! :)

GreetzZ KC`Pulse
